<br />
Next up, the real sticking point, is that the NFL wants to switch the Refs to a 401k style retirement plan, and the Refs are demanding a Pension, because that's what they've always had.  Personally I think if you're making a minimum of 110k for less than half the year, fuck you for demanding a pension.</blockquote>
